            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped aubergine</strong> to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp – this is your <strong>crispy aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1716278685355-x200.jpg",
