            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a<strong> </strong>large, wide-based,<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>with your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1716278689247-x200.jpg",
