    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is golden and crisp, remove the tray from the oven and move the aubergine to one side</p><p>Add your <strong>pine nuts</strong> to the other side of the tray, then return it to the oven for a final 2-3 min, or until the pine nuts are toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 7,
