    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Greek cheese & butter bean orzo </strong>topped with the<strong> crispy aubergine </strong>and<strong> toasted pine nuts</strong></p><p>Crumble the <strong>remaining Greek cheese</strong> all<strong> </strong>over, then drizzle with the <strong>paprika oil</strong></p><p>Season to taste with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
